message.body: Hey friend! Are you free for brunch? If so, my RJ Grp meets at 1230, so maybe we cld meet at 1130 or 45? If not no worries, we'll plan for another time! :)
Well so I have a lot of work and I am going at 11 BECAUSE I will be at haverford house for dinner tonight! Will you be there? If for some reason you wont i can stay in the DC and eat with you :)
